多重大问题。「末日之钟」由包括诺贝尔奖获得者在内的科学家和政策专家负责调整，指针越靠近午夜，表明人类文明所面临的威胁越大。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a7687321611637fc57ac8619c4c508e8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580624681"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/tux9M/h39BiEAMaCDkxMzA5NzczIJ22yJ4GMAQ4qAFAH3IJNTgwNjI0NjgxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1674828455.4547725", "card_id": "Q_575376537", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "经济学里说的「租」是什么概念？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "经济学里说的租和日常说的租赁、租金概念一样吗？ 如常见的经济租、准租、寻租等概念，要如何理解呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/575376537"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/tux9M/h39BiEAMaCDkwMTQyOTY0IMXTs50GMAI4rwFAIHIJNTc1Mzc2NTM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1674828455.4553351", "card_id": "Q_573236106", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 87}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "金庸小说里小龙女为啥要睡绳子上？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-83d1b8636ce670ea839d87c5ff7c4f9d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/573236106"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/tux9M/h39BiEAMaCDg5NjY4MTE3IOewhJ0GMAQ4owFAIXIJNTczMjM2MTA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1674828455.4558628", "card_id": "Q_580193562", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"tit